HEADWORD: Adosculation
<hw>Ad*os"cu*la"tion</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>adosculari</ets>, <ets>adosculatum</ets>, to kiss. See
